headline: Estee Lauder Posts a Higher Gross Margin Despite Tariff Pressures
summary: EL expands the second-quarter fiscal 2026 gross margin by 40 basis points to 76.5% as PRGP savings and tighter inventory help offset tariff pressure.

headline: 2 Volatile Stocks for Long-Term Investors and 1 Facing Challenges
summary: Volatility cuts both ways - while it creates opportunities, it also increases risk, making sharp declines just as likely as big gains. This unpredictability can shake out even the most experienced investors.
